RC_TUNING.yaw_dynamic_ceiling_gain.translation: The maximum gain applied to the yaw dynamic ceiling.

RC_TUNING.response_time_2.translation: Increase or decrease the response time of the rate to smooth heli movements.

ESC_PARAMETERS_FLYROTOR.cell_count.translation: Number of cells in the battery

BATTERY_CONFIG.vbatmaxcellvoltage.translation: The maximum voltage per cell before the high voltage alarm is triggered.

PID_TUNING.pid_0_F.translation: Helps push P-term based on stick input. Increasing will make response more sharp, but can cause overshoot.
